/03/09093639/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_Ineos-Grenadiers-photo-by-PocisPix_team-at-Strade-Bianche-700x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 700w\" ezoid=\"0.11756683192376971\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093639/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_Ineos-Grenadiers-photo-by-PocisPix_team-at-Strade-Bianche.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093639/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_Ineos-Grenadiers-photo-by-PocisPix_team-at-Strade-Bianche-297x178.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093639/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_Ineos-Grenadiers-photo-by-PocisPix_team-at-Strade-Bianche-800x480.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093639/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_Ineos-Grenadiers-photo-by-PocisPix_team-at-Strade-Bianche-120x72.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093639/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_Ineos-Grenadiers-photo-by-PocisPix_team-at-Strade-Bianche-768x461.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093639/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_Ineos-Grenadiers-photo-by-PocisPix_team-at-Strade-Bianche-696x418.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093639/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_Ineos-Grenadiers-photo-by-PocisPix_team-at-Strade-Bianche-1068x641.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093639/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_Ineos-Grenadiers-photo-by-PocisPix_team-at-Strade-Bianche-700x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb8 700w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-252749\">c. Kask, photo by <a href=\"https://www.pocis.pics/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PocisPix</a></figcaption></figure><p>Kask’s first new aero helmet since the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2018/01/14/kask-utopia-aero-road-bike-helmet-debuts-team-sky/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Utopia</a>, this new Wasabi looks to aim for similar aerodynamic gains, but improved versatility. Debuted in the cooler weather of early-season road racing, Kask says they expect it to work well from winter cyclocross to summer road racing, with plenty of fast gravel riding in between.</p><h3>Tech details</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093621/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_open-vs-closed.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093621/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_open-vs-closed.jpg\" alt=\"Kask Wasabi aero road helmet, adjustable venting aerodynamics merino padding, open vs. closed\" width=\"1600\" height=\"650\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093621/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_open-vs-closed.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazo