adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_open-vs-closed.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093621/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_open-vs-closed-297x121.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093621/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_open-vs-closed-800x325.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093621/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_open-vs-closed-120x49.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093621/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_open-vs-closed-768x312.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093621/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_open-vs-closed-1536x624.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093621/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_open-vs-closed-696x283.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093621/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_open-vs-closed-1068x434.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093621/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_open-vs-closed-1034x420.jpg 1034w\"></a></p><p>The Wasabi’s standout feature is the large central portion of the outer EPS shell that can be slid forward and down to limit airflow. Or pull it back to open up a large vent opening, channeling airflow directly onto the rider’s forehead for additional cooling, plus two smaller openings on the side. Kask claims the effect is a change of internal temperature of roughly 1.5°C/2.7°F when riding at the same speed.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093601/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_rear-vents..jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093601/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_rear-vents..jpg\" alt=\"Kask Wasabi aero road helmet, adjustable venting aerodynamics merino padding, rear angled\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093601/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_rear-vents..jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093601/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_rear-vents..jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093601/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_rear-vents.-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093601/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_rear-vents.-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093601/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_rear-vents.-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093601/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_rear-vents.-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093601/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_rear-vents.-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093601/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_rear-vents.-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093601/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_rear-vents.-630x420.jpg 630w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093601/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_rear-vents..jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093601/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_rear-vents.-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093601/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_rear-vents.-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093601/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_rear-vents.-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093601/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_rear-vents.-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093601/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_rear-vents.-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093601/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_rear-vents.-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093601/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_rear-vents.-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>In either case, a prominent central scoop pulls in, to flow through the helmet’s inner channels over the top of your head, and out the larger six rear-facing exhaust vents.</p><p>The aerodynamic difference from open to closed is said to be &lt;1W of drag at riding speeds of 50kph/31mph. Either way, Kask says it is “<em>one of the pro peloton’s fastest helmets – second only to Kask’s Utopia</em>“.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093542/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_inside.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093542/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_inside.jpg\" alt=\"Kask Wasabi aero road helmet, adjustable venting aerodynamics merino padding, inside\" width=\"1200\" height=\"750\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093542/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_inside.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093542/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_inside.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093542/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_insid