g-aerodynamics-merino-padding_inside-120x75.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093542/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_inside-768x480.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093542/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_inside-696x435.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093542/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_inside-1068x668.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093542/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_inside-672x420.jpg 672w\"></a></p><p>Inside, the 100% made-in-Italy Kask Wasabi uses ethically-sourced, merino wool from fellow Italian producer <a href=\"https://rewoolution.it/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Reda</a> to line its padding. Kask claims it helps offer improved thermoregulation and better wicking than synthetic pads for improved comfort.</p><p>Retention is managed by a dial-adjust Octo Fit system with Kask’s signature wide range of rear height adjustability, the same as in the top Protone or Utopia. Kask says the new Wasabi has also been <a href=\"https://www.kask.com/en/safety.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">WG11 crash-tested &amp; certified</a> to protect against both linear &amp; rotational impacts</p><h3>Kask Wasabi aero road helmet – Availability?</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093525/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-helmet_adjustable-venting-aerodynamics-merino-padding_Ineos-Grenadiers-edition-angled.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/09093525/Kask-Wasabi-aero-road-he